SUMMARY:SMR Mayapple Trail Runs
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\nRunners ar
 e invited to register for the 17th annual Mayapple Trail Runs to be held o
 n Saturday\, May 16\, 2026 in beautiful South Mountain Reservation in Esse
 x County\, N.J. based out of the Locust Grove Picnic Area\, 197 Glen Avenu
 e\, Millburn.\n\nThe races are organized by the volunteers of the South Mo
 untain Conservancy (SMC) with the support of the Essex County Parks Depart
 ment.\nThe USA Track and Field sanctioned races provide an informal but su
 pportive trail race environment for runners who are up to the challenge of
  completing 5\, 10\, or 20 miles\, or ultra-marathoon distances of 50K (31
  miles) and 50 miles. There is also an informal\, untimed one-mile race fo
 r kids 14 and under. Starting times depend on the race. The 50k and 50 mil
 e races start at 8:30. All proceeds support the mission of the Conservancy
  as a steward and advocate for the park and its public programs.\n\n## Mil
 lburn\, NJ • 50 Miler\, 50K\, 20 Miler\, 10 Miler\, 5 Miler\, Kids 1 Mil
 e Run\n\n**Registration closes: Sat\, May 16 @ 11:59PM ET**\n**To register
  as a runner or volunteer (we need you!) go to [Ultrasignup.](https://ultr
 asignup.com/register.aspx?did=135418) For very detailed descriptions and i
 nformation on group discounts\, go to our MTR [website](https://sites.goog
 le.com/view/south-mtn-mayapple-trail-runs).**\n![](https://s3.amazonaws.co
 m/img.ultrasignup.com/event/banner/ac9f4786-ce56-461c-bb7a-c6dbd288ebf0.jp
 g)[Volunteer ](https://ultrasignup.com/volunteer.aspx?dtid=65285)[Register
 ]()\n\n* [197 Glen Ave](https://www.google.com/maps?q=40.7274458\,-74.3030
 852&z=17&basemap=terrain)\n\n##\n\n*
